---

<Layout
    title="Counselling & Psychosocial Support in Bolesławiec | Online & In-Person"
    description="Practical counselling and psychosocial support in Bolesławiec and online: individual support plans, couples & family counselling, private reports/opinions, social skills training (TUS) and sensory support."
    lang="en"
>
    <Header lang="en" />

    <main class="services-page">
        <section class="page-header">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Our Services</h1>
                <p class="lead">
                    Practical counselling and psychosocial support — with clear
                    goals, actionable tools, and a plan you can use between
                    sessions.
                </p>

                <p class="lead" style="font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 0.75rem;">
                    Note: we provide educational and support-focused services
                    (non-medical). We do not conduct formal diagnosis or medical
                    treatment. If needed, we can support referral pathways and
                    cooperation with healthcare professionals.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="container services-grid">
            {
                services.map((service) => (
                    <section id={service.id} class="service-section">
                        <div class="service-header">
                            <div class="header-icon-wrapper">
                                <svg
                                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                    width="40"
                                    height="40"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    fill="none"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    stroke-width="1.5"
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                >
                                    <path d={service.icon} />
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h2>{service.title}</h2>
                            <p class="service-intro">{service.description}</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="service-details">
                            {service.details.map((detail) => (
                                <div class="detail-card">
                                    <h3>{detail.subtitle}</h3>
                                    <p>{detail.text}</p>
                                </div>
                            ))}
                        </div>
                    </section>
                ))
            }
        </div>
    </main>

    <section class="disclaimer-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="disclaimer-box">
                <h3>Important Information About Our Services</h3>
                <p>
                    Our services do not constitute medical healthcare or
                    clinical psychotherapy under medical regulations. We are an
                    interdisciplinary team of professionals (psychologists,
                    educators, counsellors) providing support through effective
                    counselling and educational techniques, modeled on best
                    practices from Anglo-Saxon systems.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Counselling complements clinical psychotherapy but does not
                    replace it. In cases requiring pharmacological treatment or
                    hospitalization, we refer clients to appropriate public
                    health facilities. Our specialists undergo regular
                    supervision to ensure effective and ethical practice. By
                    using our services, you acknowledge and accept this scope of
                    cooperation.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to start?</h2>
            <p>
                Book an appointment online — or explore the right service for
                your situation.
            </p>
            <a
                href="https://rejestracja.psychopedagog.org/#/booking"
                class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener">Book online</a
            >
        </div>
    </section>

    <section
        class="testimonials-preview"
        style="margin-top: 4rem; text-align: center;"
    >
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Why Choose Our Support Centre?</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>Experienced Specialists</h3>
                    <p>
                        A multidisciplinary team (counsellors, educators,
                        psychologists, dietitians) and structured methods
                        focused on real-life change.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>Individual Support Plans</h3>
                    <p>
                        We work with goals, steps, and everyday tools — so you
                        can practise between sessions.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <h3>Online & In-Person Sessions</h3>
                    <p>
                        Sessions in Bolesławiec and online — flexible, discreet,
                        and tailored to your schedule.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<Footer lang="en" />

<style>
    .page-header {
        background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
        padding: 4rem 0;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .lead {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .service-section {
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
    }

    .service-header {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column; /* Mobile first: Stacked */
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .service-header {
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
        }
    }

    .header-icon-wrapper {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        background: var(--color-primary-light);
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 50%;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .service-header h2 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .service-details {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Mobile first: Single column full width */
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 600px) {
        .service-details {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }
    }

    .detail-card {
        background: var(--color-bg-card);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .detail-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }

    .detail-card h3 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
        background: var(--color-primary);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 4rem 0;
        margin-top: 4rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }

    .cta-section h2 {
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-section p {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .btn-lg {
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        background: var(--color-bg-card);
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .feature {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .feature h3 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .disclaimer-section {
        margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .disclaimer-box {
        background-color: var(--color-bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-primary-light);
        border-right: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    .disclaimer-box h3 {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .disclaimer-box p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .disclaimer-box p:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }
</style>
